# Build context is the monorepo root (see packages/bot/Dockerfile).

# dependencies & build output — reinstalled / recompiled inside the image
**/node_modules
**/build
**/dist
**/dist-test
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# secrets & local state — must never enter an image layer
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/token
**/data/database.sqlite*
**/data/*.bak

# vcs & repo meta
.git
.github
.gitignore
**/.claude

# docs / planning — not needed at runtime
**/docs
MIGRATION-PLAN.md
**/README.md
